name: les lunes en sagittaire
description: which means "the moons in sagittarius". But in French, "Lune" (moon) is also an old slang word used to call the butt. And "en s'agitèrent", which sounds exactly like "in sagittarius", could be translated by "were shaken by this". So the whole caption sounds like "moons in sagittarius" but reads "the butt was shaken by this".
